Timing and subtitles brought to you by The Imperial Coroners @ Viki.com

2
00:00:10,520 --> 00:00:13,160
Xu Rugui follows Qin Luan's orders.

3
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:16,530
For all these years, he's been secretly investigating my father.

4
00:00:16,530 --> 00:00:17,819
Xiao Heng escaped.

5
00:00:17,819 --> 00:00:19,789
Catch him.

6
00:00:19,790 --> 00:00:24,689
There must be more secrets behind the Military Commissioner of Jiannan's usurp.

7
00:00:24,689 --> 00:00:28,240
Qin Luan must have held something back from the imperial court.

8
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:31,339
Maybe we can only find the answer

9
00:00:31,339 --> 00:00:34,120
when we decipher the mysteries my father left behind.

10
00:00:39,470 --> 00:00:41,299
Sir Witch Doctor drew these.

11
00:00:41,299 --> 00:00:42,939
He likes to draw?

12
00:00:42,939 --> 00:00:45,629
He didn't like it so much.

13
00:00:45,630 --> 00:00:49,349
But right before he left, he somehow started to like it.

14
00:00:49,350 --> 00:00:50,479
He drew nothing else.

15
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:52,489
He just drew mountains and trees.

16
00:00:52,489 --> 00:00:55,630
These are the views of Guanling County.

17
00:00:55,630 --> 00:00:57,519
The mountain is Phoenix Mountain.

18
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:59,950
The river is Yong'an River.

19
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:03,700
The light.

20
00:01:11,740 --> 00:01:14,529
Your Highness, what's on your mind?

21
00:01:14,529 --> 00:01:17,770
Does he always have such thick window paper?

22
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:22,029
No. It might have started when he began to like drawing.

23
00:01:22,029 --> 00:01:24,359
At that time, he bought many drawing papers.

24
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:27,049
Some were used to draw. Others were used as window paper.

25
00:01:27,049 --> 00:01:31,159
He said it was windy at night. Air wouldn't come through if window paper was thick.

26
00:01:34,060 --> 00:01:37,880
Chu Chu, pull down the curtains.

27
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:59,099
[The Imperial Coroner]

28
00:01:59,100 --> 00:02:02,900
[Episode 18]

29
00:02:11,890 --> 00:02:13,429
Your Highness, it's done.

30
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:16,220
See if the other side's wall is different.

31
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:19,539
- The wall?
- Yes.

32
00:02:30,270 --> 00:02:31,519
Your Highness, come take a look.

33
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,720
There's a small bright spot on the wall.

34
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,429
I found it.

35
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:58,399
There's a small hole that has penetrated the wall.

36
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,629
It was covered by both sides' drawing paper.

37
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:03,069
When the room is dim,

38
00:03:03,070 --> 00:03:04,799
if we light candles in the other side's cabinet,

39
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,909
the candle light will

40
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:10,109
cast this bright spot on this side's drawing paper.

41
00:03:10,110 --> 00:03:12,820
Did Sir Witch Doctor do this?

42
00:03:14,450 --> 00:03:16,269
In the previous Sui Dynasty, construction was often performed.

43
00:03:16,270 --> 00:03:19,559
Once, 300,000 taels of construction fee got lost abruptly during transport.
[Rapid constructions]

44
00:03:19,559 --> 00:03:21,430
They found no trace of it
[Transporting construction fund]

45
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:23,859
until the judge found out how they hid the money.

46
00:03:23,859 --> 00:03:27,279
Then, the world knew the truth.
[Judge]

47
00:03:27,279 --> 00:03:28,659
The ministers involved in the case
[Notice]

48
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:31,089
used the principle of Borrowed Light.
[Truth came to light]

49
00:03:31,090 --> 00:03:33,759
They used the tavern wall and the paintings to

50
00:03:33,759 --> 00:03:36,769
design a map to mark the location where they hid the money.
[Borrowed light]

51
00:03:36,769 --> 00:03:38,879
So they can split booty afterward.

52
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:41,020
[Treasure]

53
00:03:42,090 --> 00:03:43,629
This case was adapted into novels

54
00:03:43,629 --> 00:03:45,659
and was spread widely across the nation.

55
00:03:45,660 --> 00:03:48,870
I think my father learned this trick from it.

56
00:03:54,570 --> 00:03:58,289
Your Highness, something went wrong with the Chu family.

57
00:03:58,289 --> 00:03:59,790
Let's go.

58
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:03,210
Your Highness.

59
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:10,779
It's my fault. Please punish me.

60
00:04:10,779 --> 00:04:12,109
Grandfather, are you all right?

61
00:04:12,110 --> 00:04:14,629
I'm fine. But your brother is missing.

62
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,859
Grandfather, don't worry.

63
00:04:15,859 --> 00:04:17,509
His Highness is here. My brother will be fine.

64
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:19,229
What happened? Who did this?

65
00:04:19,230 --> 00:04:22,009
- Where is Xu Rugui?
- Your Highness, we don't know what happened earlier.

66
00:04:22,009 --> 00:04:24,709
Xu Rugui suddenly broke free from the ropes, attacked us, and tried to run away.

67
00:04:24,709 --> 00:04:28,109
When we were fighting, these people who dressed like bandits broke in.

68
00:04:28,109 --> 00:04:30,509
Xu Rugui was obviously their target. We were outnumbered.

69
00:04:30,509 --> 00:04:31,999
Xu Rugui escaped amid the chaos.

70
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,549
The bandits went to pursue Xu Rugui. Zhang Yun went after them.

71
00:04:34,549 --> 00:04:37,820
I stayed here to ensure the Chu family's safety.

72
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:48,759
[Rope File]
[Cut]

73
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,739
- Where is Chu He?
- We didn't notice that.

74
00:04:50,739 --> 00:04:52,719
We also didn't hear another fight.

75
00:04:52,719 --> 00:04:55,729
We only found Chu He missing, when the Chu family's seniors asked us.

76
00:04:55,730 --> 00:04:58,869
Don't worry, Your Highness. I've already asked people from the County Office to pursue them.

77
00:04:58,869 --> 00:05:01,169
- How many bandits ran away?
- Two.

78
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,899
Chu He spent time alone with Xu Rugui?

79
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:22,059
Yes, Your Highness.

80
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:23,479
Chu He brought food to Xu Rugui.

81
00:05:23,479 --> 00:05:26,890
He spent around 30 minutes alone with Xu Rugui.

82
00:05:26,890 --> 00:05:28,840
Chu He?

83
00:05:32,820 --> 00:05:34,819
This is a tool for carpenter work.

84
00:05:34,820 --> 00:05:37,249
Xu Rugui must have used this to cut the rope.

85
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:39,620
Why would Chu He help Xu Rugui escape?

86
00:05:57,690 --> 00:06:00,879
Why did you allow Chu He and Xu Rugui to spend time alone?  You—

87
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:03,939
It's my fault. Your Highness, please punish us.

88
00:06:05,450 --> 00:06:06,749
Your Highness.

89
00:06:06,749 --> 00:06:10,349
Chu Chu, inspect the bodies first.

90
00:06:10,349 --> 00:06:11,850
Okay.

91
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,439
The dead is well built.

92
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:23,599
There are thick calluses on his palms which were formed because of training.

93
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:26,330
The wound on his chest is fatal.

94
00:06:36,470 --> 00:06:39,860
This man has the same calluses.

95
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:47,109
These people were soldiers.

96
00:06:47,110 --> 00:06:48,910
Soldiers?

97
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:53,109
I can tell from the calluses on their palms.

98
00:06:53,110 --> 00:06:55,619
These were formed from years of training as soldiers.

99
00:06:55,619 --> 00:06:58,579
The training for soldiers is different from the training of martial art learners.

100
00:06:58,579 --> 00:07:01,509
So the calluses are different, too.

101
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:02,789
Soldiers?

102
00:07:02,790 --> 00:07:06,100
Are they Shence soldiers sent by Qin Luan to silence Xu Rugui?
(Shence Army was a Tang dynasty army unit, based in Chang'an, forming the core of the imperial guards responsible for protecting the emperor.)

103
00:07:09,110 --> 00:07:11,540
The group of people who broke in first had Shence Army's fighting skills.

104
00:07:11,550 --> 00:07:14,010
But those who broke in later are weird.

105
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:24,670
Xu Rugui broke free from the rope and fought with us.

106
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,609
At that moment, the first group broke in.

107
00:07:30,609 --> 00:07:33,030
They were determined to kill Xu Rugui.

108
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:42,999
Then the next group broke in.

109
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,349
They didn't try to kill Xu Rugui.

110
00:07:44,350 --> 00:07:46,530
On the contrary, they tried to protect him.

111
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:50,979
These two groups of people also engaged in fights themselves.

112
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:53,920
Those who tried to kill Xu Rugui

113
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:56,029
were from the Shence Army.

114
00:07:56,030 --> 00:07:59,439
The other group were here to catch him.

115
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,509
Catch him?

116
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:02,139
That's weird.

117
00:08:02,139 --> 00:08:05,109
No, it isn't. This is the fight between the snipe and the mussel.

118
00:08:05,109 --> 00:08:07,550
The snipe and the mussel?

119
00:08:07,550 --> 00:08:09,549
Qin Luan's Rugui House is the buyer.

120
00:08:09,550 --> 00:08:11,789
Those who committed the crimes at Qianzhou are the seller.

121
00:08:11,790 --> 00:08:14,439
This originally should be a trade that benefited both parties.

122
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:16,199
Now, Rugui House's case has been solved.

123
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:18,199
They're now the snipe and the mussel.

124
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:22,349
Now, the mussel knows everything about Rugui House.

125
00:08:22,350 --> 00:08:25,669
They want to control Xu Rugui and use him as leverage

126
00:08:25,670 --> 00:08:27,729
to become the buyer.

127
00:08:27,729 --> 00:08:30,639
What are you talking about? I'm so confused.

128
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:33,319
How can you be confused? Let me explain it.

129
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:37,089
His Highness means that there are two parties of bad people.

130
00:08:37,090 --> 00:08:39,029
- Two parties?
- Yes.

131
00:08:39,029 --> 00:08:40,859
One side wanted to kill people.

132
00:08:40,859 --> 00:08:43,749
But they were unwilling to do it themselves. So they paid for hitmen.

133
00:08:43,749 --> 00:08:47,179
The other group of people commits murders for money.

134
00:08:47,180 --> 00:08:50,719
Think about it. Killing for money is supposed to be a secret.

135
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:54,449
So, the buyer just knows whether the target has been killed or not.

136
00:08:54,449 --> 00:08:57,219
They won't know who does it.

137
00:08:57,219 --> 00:08:59,859
But now His Highness has shut down Rugui House.

138
00:08:59,859 --> 00:09:02,859
The buyers now know Xu Rugui is the one who collected the money.

139
00:09:02,859 --> 00:09:08,199
So, the buyer discovered that Qin Luan is behind Xu Rugui

140
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:11,510
and tried to use Xu Rugui to threaten Qin Luan.

141
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:14,700
I get it. Then this is a double-cross.

142
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,199
That's right.

143
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,909
Clear the floor first.

144
00:09:17,909 --> 00:09:20,359
Jinli, your men are more familiar with this neighborhood.

145
00:09:20,359 --> 00:09:23,179
Please send more men to search for Chu He.

146
00:09:23,180 --> 00:09:25,539
Oh. Take Chu He's dog with you.

147
00:09:25,540 --> 00:09:28,619
It's familiar with Chu He's scent. It can somehow help.

148
00:09:28,619 --> 00:09:32,029
Xu Rugui was badly wounded after this fight.

149
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:33,569
He can't go far.

150
00:09:33,570 --> 00:09:35,609
Pay attention to the hiding spots nearby.

151
00:09:35,610 --> 00:09:37,110
Okay.

152
00:09:38,810 --> 00:09:41,459
Jing Yi. Leng Yue. Go to the County Office and bring more people.

153
00:09:41,459 --> 00:09:46,089
Clear this area. Just tell them the bandits attacked. Nothing more.

154
00:09:46,130 --> 00:09:47,630
- Yes.
- Okay.

155
00:09:49,410 --> 00:09:52,590
Chu Chu, come with me.

156
00:10:23,450 --> 00:10:24,779
What?

157
00:10:24,780 --> 00:10:27,149
Didn't you hear it? There was a breathing sound.

158
00:10:27,149 --> 00:10:28,410
Someone has been following us.

159
00:10:28,410 --> 00:10:31,209
No. You must have made a mistake.

160
00:10:31,209 --> 00:10:32,639
It's our own breathing sound.

161
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:35,250
Xu Rugui is just ahead of us. Hurry.

162
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:37,549
Xu Rugui is very cunning.

163
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:39,670
Beware of his traps.

164
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:43,950
So annoying.

165
00:11:13,350 --> 00:11:15,669
The forest is rainy. The road is muddy.

166
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:18,379
The passersby will leave foot tracks. Observe the road.

167
00:11:18,379 --> 00:11:19,880
Yes!

168
00:11:33,450 --> 00:11:37,600
Your Highness, actually I...

169
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,559
You already know, don't you?

170
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:41,299
What should I know?

171
00:11:41,299 --> 00:11:42,879
About my father and mother.

172
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:44,709
You've interrogated Xu Rugui.

173
00:11:44,710 --> 00:11:47,000
So, you must know everything.

174
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:50,079
He did say something about your father and mother.

175
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,959
But those haven't been verified.

176
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:54,959
After I verify it, I'll tell you everything honestly.

177
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:58,650
Did he tell you that my father is

178
00:11:58,650 --> 00:12:02,220
the rebel, Yun Yi?

179
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:04,500
Yes.

180
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:08,029
But it's just his one-sided accusations.

181
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,709
We can't come to a conclusion for now.

182
00:12:09,710 --> 00:12:13,309
Can you tell me the things you have verified about my father and mother?

183
00:12:13,309 --> 00:12:14,609
Xu Rugui is lying, right?

184
00:12:14,609 --> 00:12:17,030
Bad people all lie, right?

185
00:12:22,340 --> 00:12:28,389
I went to the Xu Mansion to look for you because Xu Rugui left this hairpin behind.

186
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:34,649
You're saying that Xu Rugui intentionally left this at the scene for you?

187
00:12:34,649 --> 00:12:36,860
Why would he do that?

188
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:38,419
At first, I didn't understand either.

189
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:41,379
So I rushed back to the County Office and looked through your mother's bequest.

190
00:12:41,379 --> 00:12:45,039
And I found out that your father might be an officer who worked for the Military Commissioner of Jiannan.

191
00:12:45,039 --> 00:12:47,270
Then I understood his intention.

192
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:49,320
What is it?

193
00:12:49,810 --> 00:12:52,860
He led me on the investigation of your father,

194
00:12:52,860 --> 00:12:55,040
hoping it can destroy our trust in each other

195
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:58,179
and force you to leave and become a part of his team.

196
00:12:58,180 --> 00:13:02,859
So, what Xu Rugui said is real?

197
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:04,219
I told you.

198
00:13:04,220 --> 00:13:07,319
It hasn't been verified. So we can't reach a conclusion.

199
00:13:07,319 --> 00:13:11,000
But you've already deduced that he might be an officer for the Military Commissioner of Jiannan.

200
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:16,739
Then... is he the rebel, Yun Yi, that Xu Rugui talked about?

201
00:13:16,740 --> 00:13:18,859
That's exactly why Xu Rugui is cunning.

202
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:22,029
He wanted me to discover this when I was looking for you.

203
00:13:22,029 --> 00:13:26,329
I would easily forget that my original intention was to search for your whereabouts.

204
00:13:26,329 --> 00:13:29,609
Instead, I would go on an investigation to see whether your father was the rebel.

205
00:13:29,609 --> 00:13:32,519
In that case, he would have more time to get out of the pursuit.

206
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,659
But, Your Highness—

207
00:13:33,660 --> 00:13:38,129
Chu Chu, finding your whereabouts is different from the investigation of your father's identity.

208
00:13:38,129 --> 00:13:43,599
The only connection is the fact that Xu Rugui wants to use it to distract me.

209
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:46,049
What about now?

210
00:13:46,050 --> 00:13:50,690
If my father is really the rebel, Yun Yi, will I get you in trouble?

211
00:14:01,130 --> 00:14:02,129
Jinli.

212
00:14:02,130 --> 00:14:04,299
General Xiao, why are you here?

213
00:14:04,300 --> 00:14:06,639
This road leads to the mountain.

214
00:14:06,639 --> 00:14:09,049
Are you going to the mountain area to look for my brother?

215
00:14:09,050 --> 00:14:11,050
What happened?

216
00:14:11,050 --> 00:14:13,659
Chu He might have fallen into the river by accident.

217
00:14:13,660 --> 00:14:15,859
A clear mark at the upper stream's riverside indicated that someone fell into the water.

218
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:17,979
The mark is roughly the same size as Chu He's footprint.

219
00:14:17,980 --> 00:14:21,469
When we reached the spot, we also heard a scream from Chu He.

220
00:14:21,470 --> 00:14:25,339
And this dog's reaction also confirmed that Chu He was once there.

221
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:28,149
But after that, we found no trace of him.

222
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:31,139
My brother is a good swimmer. He can get back to shore soon.

223
00:14:31,139 --> 00:14:33,099
Chu Chu, don't worry.

224
00:14:33,099 --> 00:14:35,399
Chu He might have swum to the opposite riverside.

225
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:38,379
I was talking to Chu Chu back then. We didn't pay attention to the river.

226
00:14:38,379 --> 00:14:40,519
He might have swum to the other side.

227
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:44,739
Jinli, please take some men and search the opposite riverside.

228
00:14:44,740 --> 00:14:46,469
This row. Go search the other side.

229
00:14:46,470 --> 00:14:47,870
Yes.

230
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:52,230
Jinyu, come over here.

231
00:15:03,690 --> 00:15:04,999
What?

232
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,549
I haven't had time to talk about this with you.

233
00:15:07,550 --> 00:15:09,229
Chu He made such a scene.

234
00:15:09,230 --> 00:15:11,569
I think it's about that case.

235
00:15:11,570 --> 00:15:14,459
We don't have time to waste. Just say it.

236
00:15:15,350 --> 00:15:19,239
I accidentally heard Chu He and his father's conversation in the kitchen.

237
00:15:19,239 --> 00:15:23,049
If I marry Chu Chu, she will be my wife then.

238
00:15:23,050 --> 00:15:26,469
Whether she accepts the family or not, she is part of the Chu family.

239
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:30,219
Even if you want to, you have to get the approval of Chu Chu.

240
00:15:30,219 --> 00:15:31,859
Ridiculous! He is...

241
00:15:31,859 --> 00:15:33,419
What?

242
00:15:33,419 --> 00:15:35,839
They're not related by blood.

243
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:40,379
And over the past days, by my observation, I think he truly has feelings for Chu Chu.

244
00:15:40,379 --> 00:15:42,710
And today's incident.

245
00:15:42,710 --> 00:15:44,169
Today's incident?

246
00:15:44,170 --> 00:15:46,199
What are your concerns?

247
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:49,149
You found a filing blade in the coffin workshop, right?

248
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:52,439
The guards also said that Chu He spent some time alone with Xu Rugui.

249
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:56,899
Maybe, Chu He found out that Xu Rugui is Miss Chu's uncle.

250
00:15:56,899 --> 00:15:59,339
He's worried that Xu Rugui may take her away,

251
