How interesting.

508
00:32:53,760 --> 00:32:55,539
I'm free today.

509
00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:57,749
So I want to play chess with you.

510
00:32:57,750 --> 00:33:00,559
However, you went to the palace early in the morning.

511
00:33:00,560 --> 00:33:02,709
I heard that you had a long conversation

512
00:33:02,710 --> 00:33:05,570
with His Majesty at Jiangshan Hall?

513
00:33:06,250 --> 00:33:10,740
Seems that nothing can escape Senior Jing's observation.

514
00:33:14,950 --> 00:33:18,300
I have begged His Majesty

515
00:33:18,300 --> 00:33:20,649
to allow me to visit the Southwest soon.

516
00:33:20,650 --> 00:33:22,569
Commandery Prince An left the capital.

517
00:33:22,570 --> 00:33:24,559
Her Grace is worried for him.

518
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:26,809
Her Grace came to visit me many times because of that.

519
00:33:26,809 --> 00:33:30,749
Senior Jing, have you heard any news?

520
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:32,059
The situation in the Southwest is complicated.

521
00:33:32,060 --> 00:33:35,409
I'm worried that His Highness might be in an adverse situation.

522
00:33:35,410 --> 00:33:36,869
Yes.

523
00:33:36,870 --> 00:33:39,879
Commandery Prince An is discreet.

524
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:44,749
But they had no experience working with local officers.

525
00:33:44,750 --> 00:33:47,509
This indeed makes us worried.

526
00:33:47,510 --> 00:33:49,980
Senior Jing, you're right.

527
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:54,620
Illegal copper coin case involves many parties.

528
00:33:54,620 --> 00:33:58,489
Commandery Prince An hasn't reported to the imperial court yet.

529
00:33:58,490 --> 00:34:02,229
I don't know if he's found out anything yet.

530
00:34:02,230 --> 00:34:07,269
I'm worried that if the Leng family from the Southwest is involved in it...

531
00:34:07,269 --> 00:34:11,829
Commandery Prince An has always been prudent.

532
00:34:11,830 --> 00:34:14,709
He won't put himself in danger.

533
00:34:14,710 --> 00:34:16,459
That's right.

534
00:34:16,459 --> 00:34:20,269
Their trip to the Southwest is for Prince Consort.

535
00:34:20,270 --> 00:34:24,529
If they can find Prince Consort, who has been missing for years,

536
00:34:24,530 --> 00:34:27,329
then the thousand-mile trip wasn't made in vain.

537
00:34:27,330 --> 00:34:29,279
I'm afraid it won't be that easy.

538
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:31,580
Senior Jing, what are you worried about?

539
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:34,029
Nothing.

540
00:34:34,030 --> 00:34:36,949
I was just thinking if it's that easy,

541
00:34:36,950 --> 00:34:40,031
