Your Highness.

544
00:34:59,020 --> 00:35:00,369
How's Chu He doing?

545
00:35:00,369 --> 00:35:03,229
Leng Yue said he's fine. She went to buy medicine for him.

546
00:35:07,600 --> 00:35:10,400
Chu Chu, go home first.

547
00:35:11,460 --> 00:35:12,739
But my brother...

548
00:35:12,740 --> 00:35:16,129
Chu Chu, don't worry. We're here.

549
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:18,919
